data.description: Come experience the South Florida lifestyle in the highly desirable golf community of Hammock Creek designed by Jack Nicklaus. Being the only courtyard pool home currently available in the neighborhood it won't last long. This spacious 3bd/3ba home is move in ready & is perfect for entertaining. Enter through the double gates to a fabulous patio centered on a beautiful pool/spa and a detached 1/1 guest house. The main house has 2bd/2ba, large family room, formal living and dining rooms and separate screened in patio. The master suite has private access to the pool area thru the sliding glass doors or master bath. The kitchen is centrally located in the home with newer refrigerator, granite countertops, eat in counter and breakfast nook. Additional features: new A/C, Additional features: new A/C, laminate floors, built in closets, updated security system, electric shades in the master, floored attic space, exterior paint. No golf membership required!
